Description: Xwayland outside your Wayland
 xwayland-satellite grants rootless Xwayland integration to any Wayland
 compositor implementing xdg_wm_base and viewporter. This is
 particularly useful for compositors that (understandably) do not want
 to go through implementing support for rootless Xwayland themselves.

